songs.title: IDGAF
songs.lyrics:
Verse 1 [Bohemia]

Champagne pee ke Raja kudiyan de naal nacha
Fresh mere hisse di baad ch fir kisse di
Rap karan munde hun loki mainu kehnde sun
Mere ton suni jaaye na bakwaas hun kisse di
Mera sangeet main chadeya 3 saal vekho
Mundean ne rap da kitta haal ve tussi
Jinni marji vi hun speed vadha lo
Raftaar meri sohni rap karo ya gaa lo
CDiyan banwalo show karwalo
Poster chapwa ke lagwa lo par yaad rakkho
Jis din bhi aana mera jahaaz
Tuhaanu hawa ch uda jana mera jahaaz

Hook [Haji Springer]

On the ground 24/7
Hit your city in a 747
Big dogs driving big trucks
Its the city giving big bucks

I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***

Verse 2 [Bohemia]

Phir kehndee Raja poll khole
Moriyan ch chuhe paande raule
Te appan je de baaz
Chubareyan ch saanu tuhaadi aundi nahi awaaz
Lehaaz main kitta par tussi aaye na baaz
Aanda mera jahaz..
Note kama ke janda mera jahaaz
Bael gaddi teri jaandi jinni dur ohna
Take off ch le jaanda mera jahaaz

Hun baadlan ton utte sitaareyan vall
Utthon bai ke thalle vekha tuhaade saareya vall
Je mein haariyan kal mera kakh ni jana
Hun paira ch main bina juraaban de ferragamo pana

On the ground 24/7
Hit your city in a 747
Big dogs driving big trucks
Its the city giving big bucks

Hook [Haji Springer]

I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***
I don't give a F***
